videos.description: Galen Robinson hits the deck to get the steal and finds Armoni Brooks for the and-1 layup.
videos.headline: Robinson's hustle leads to Brooks' bucket

videos.description: Rob Gray drives past a couple of defenders and finishes with the acrobatic layup for the and-1.
videos.headline: Gray weaves through traffic for the layup

videos.description: Galen Robinson dishes a nice pass to a wide-open Chris Harris Jr. and he throws down the and-1 slam.
videos.headline: Harris dunks through contact
